<tt><font size="2">SECTION &quot;A&quot;: COST OF ADMINISTRATION</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">AND COMPLIANCE</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">---------------------------------------------------------------------</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">1. It avoids requiring a &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;NO &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; YES</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;valuation of listed</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;securities and</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;commodities at the end</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;of each year</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">2. It avoids requiring a &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;YES &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;YES</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;valuation of unlisted</font></tt><br>
<tt><font size="2">&nbsp; &nbsp;securities at the end</font></tt><br>
